 Kandarp Gajjar, CE, LDRP-ITR, KSV

🏆 Best Presentation Award
 Congratulations to Princy Patel and Kandarp Gajjar for delivering an outstanding presentation and earning the Best Presentation recognition!
We applaud the dedication and hard work of our students in pursuing research opportunities at esteemed national institutions. These experiences reflect our commitment to nurturing future researchers and innovators.
